        " أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ اَلسِّهَامُ اِرْتَفَعَتِ اَلشُّفْعَةُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3376 - Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said: \"When the shares are divided, the right of preemption (shufah) is annulled.\""
        ]
